data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity to experience active adult living in Arizona at it's finest! This 2 bed, 2 bath plus office home offers AMAZING MOUNTAIN VIEWS and is located on a corner lot with a large common space next to it! This popular Bolero Floor Plan is move-in ready and has a three car split garage with tons of storage cabinets! From the private courtyard in the front to the spacious great room and kitchen area, there is no shortage of space to entertain guests. Plus there is a large formal dining room, that could be used as a game room or formal living area. The primary on suite is oversized with a bay window, his and her vanities, deep soaker tub, and large walk-in closet. You will never get tired of the views!! Plus the home offers GRANDFATHERED NET METERED SOLAR to help you save $$$ on your electric bills! Bills average only $145/month for full time living! CantaMia is nestled in the Estrella Mountains and offers a guard gated entrance, beautiful walking paths around the lakes, heated indoor and outdoor pools, pickleball courts, billiards, fitness facility, art studio, numerous clubs and activities and café/bar. Come and experience all this community has to offer!
